Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.36,0:01:36.24,Episode-Title,Text,0000,0000,0000,,Episode 11\N"Piano"
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.06,0:01:36.24,Main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,You surprised me.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.76,0:01:37.76,Main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,I'm happy,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.47,0:01:39.49,Main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,but...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.07,0:01:45.87,Main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,Kakeru-kun, I wonder if you really like me.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.89,0:01:50.89,Main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,I—
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.51,0:01:52.44,Main,Kakeru,0000,0000,0000,,Am I
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.30,0:01:56.30,Main,Kakeru,0000,0000,0000,,just trying to make myself think I like you?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.16,0:01:58.05,Main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,Are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.98,0:02:02.34,Main,Kakeru,0000,0000,0000,,Am I just trying to validate myself?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.14,0:02:06.82,Main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,It's still snowing around me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.82,0:02:09.43,Main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,But you can't see it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.15,0:02:12.77,Main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,We don't understand anything \Nabout each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.83,0:02:14.79,Main,Kakeru,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.36,0:02:17.11,Main,Kakeru,0000,0000,0000,,I don't see the snow.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.21,0:02:28.34,Main,Kakeru,0000,0000,0000,,I'm hoping to get my mom \Nto play piano for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.78,0:02:30.09,Main,Kakeru,0000,0000,0000,,I want you to come, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.61,0:02:32.06,Main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,Your mom's piano?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.44,0:02:33.44,Main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,That's great.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.88,0:02:37.95,Main,Kakeru,0000,0000,0000,,She's a professional. I think \Nshe'll take it seriously.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.30,0:02:39.15,Main,Kakeru,0000,0000,0000,,Then—
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.53,0:02:42.09,Main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,Then, what?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.37,0:02:44.05,Main,Kakeru,0000,0000,0000,,I want you to come.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.81,0:02:48.53,Main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,Will we learn something about \Nthe two of us if we're there?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.60,0:02:51.25,Main,Kakeru,0000,0000,0000,,I'll call Mom now.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.81,0:02:53.02,Main,Kakeru,0000,0000,0000,,Let's ask her to do it tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.69,0:02:56.24,Main,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Okikura speaking.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.24,0:02:57.14,Italics,Kakeru,0000,0000,0000,,Mom?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.14,0:02:59.12,Main,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Kakeru? What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.42,0:03:01.23,Italics,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,I have a new friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.53,0:03:04.16,Italics,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,Could you play the piano for her?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.48,0:03:06.36,Main,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,That's an unusual request.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.36,0:03:08.79,Main,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,It's the first time you've \Never said anything like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.79,0:03:09.58,Italics,Kakeru,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.96,0:03:11.07,Main,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.07,0:03:13.64,Main,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,I might as well play a few pieces.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.95,0:03:16.37,Main,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't you invite her parents, \Ntoo, if they're available?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.67,0:03:17.63,Italics,Kakeru,0000,0000,0000,,Good idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.01,0:03:19.10,Italics,Kakeru,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks, Mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.03,0:03:20.93,Main,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Kakeru,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.06,0:03:24.64,Main,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,so, about what we were talking about.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.17,0:03:26.20,Italics,Kakeru,0000,0000,0000,,What about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.64,0:03:28.22,Main,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Want to come with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.07,0:03:31.01,Main,Kakeru,0000,0000,0000,,I'm thinking about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.83,0:03:34.71,Italics,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Your friend that lent you this phone—
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.71,0:03:36.11,Italics,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Fukami-san, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.11,0:03:38.97,Italics,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,I met her once.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.97,0:03:41.73,Italics,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,She came by when you \Nhappened not to be home.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.17,0:03:43.20,Main,Kakeru,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.58,0:03:44.66,Main,Kakeru,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.68,0:03:47.62,Main,Kakeru,0000,0000,0000,,She's kind and indecisive.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.41,0:03:51.71,Italics,Kakeru,0000,0000,0000,,She gets pushed around. \NShe has trouble with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.40,0:03:54.75,Italics,Kakeru,0000,0000,0000,,And I'm making her even more confused.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.17,0:03:58.30,Italics,Kakeru,0000,0000,0000,,She made me realize I don't know anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.20,0:04:01.17,Main,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,I see. You like her.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.31,0:04:02.85,Main,Kakeru,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.83,0:04:08.64,Main,Kakeru,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go home.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.86,0:04:13.56,Main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,I'll stay here a little longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.09,0:04:19.02,Main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,I feel like this summer started here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.97,0:04:21.43,Main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,I want to stay here longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.43,0:04:23.99,Main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,This is my place, I think.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.38,0:04:26.21,Main,Kakeru,0000,0000,0000,,Your place?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.51,0:04:28.31,Main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,Sacchan told me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.01,0:04:30.46,Main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,The season,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.87,0:04:32.80,Main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,and the time, and the people you're with,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.80,0:04:35.73,Main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,make an ordinary place special.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.00,0:04:40.46,Main,Kakeru,0000,0000,0000,,You should go home before it gets too late.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.46,0:04:41.26,Main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.91,0:04:44.72,Main,Kakeru,0000,0000,0000,,See you tomorrow afternoon, at my place.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.79,0:04:46.51,Main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,Got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.93,0:05:03.07,Main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,Hina-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.42,0:05:04.93,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.93,0:05:07.19,Main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be home by tomorrow morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.49,0:05:10.49,Main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,Make sure Mom and Dad don't \Nget too worried. Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.72,0:05:13.17,Main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,Please. Okay, I'm hanging up.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.90,0:05:18.88,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,Onee-chan, oh no!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.12,0:05:37.39,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,I'm home.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.39,0:05:39.59,Main,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome. You're late.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.67,0:05:42.18,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.28,0:05:46.49,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome home, Onee-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.24,0:05:52.40,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,I hope she's doing well.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.82,0:05:54.45,Main,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Dinner, you two.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.75,0:05:55.80,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,Coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.31,0:06:00.58,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,Onee-chan says she'll eat later.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.41,0:06:12.43,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks for the food.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.96,0:06:15.89,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,She says she's not too hungry today, \Nso she only needs a little.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.34,0:06:18.24,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,That sister of mine's so selfish.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.54,0:06:19.27,Main,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.56,0:06:25.73,Main,Sachi,0000,0000,0000,,I want to go to the mountains again.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.91,0:06:30.56,Italics,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah? Mountains are nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.92,0:06:32.85,Italics,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if Nee-chan can make it this week.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.85,0:06:35.33,Main,Sachi,0000,0000,0000,,No, I want to hike from the bottom.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.89,0:06:42.94,Main,Yanagi,0000,0000,0000,,How's your
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.92,0:06:45.67,Main,Yanagi,0000,0000,0000,,knee?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.14,0:06:49.53,Main,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,The trainer who's been helping me out
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.53,0:06:51.71,Main,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,says it's a lot better now.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.20,0:06:52.91,Main,Yanagi,0000,0000,0000,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.71,0:06:55.19,Main,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,I'm glad I went to training camp.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.96,0:06:58.37,Main,Yanagi,0000,0000,0000,,Are you joining the club \Nagain second semester?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.10,0:07:01.57,Main,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,Coach says I should.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.18,0:07:03.33,Main,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,I think I will.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.98,0:07:05.77,Main,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.29,0:07:09.67,Main,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,I don't really know what Yanagi's doing.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.14,0:07:12.82,Main,Yanagi,0000,0000,0000,,Want to come watch my lessons?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.60,0:07:40.31,Main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,You didn't go home?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.63,0:07:42.37,Main,Kakeru,0000,0000,0000,,That's my line.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.73,0:07:44.88,Main,Kakeru,0000,0000,0000,,You were supposed to go home after a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.49,0:08:17.76,Main,Kakeru,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if this'll become
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.32,0:08:20.15,Main,Kakeru,0000,0000,0000,,my place if I stay here all night.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.18,0:08:22.30,Main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,Well—
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.63,0:08:24.38,Main,Kakeru,0000,0000,0000,,If I had my own place...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.51,0:08:28.98,Main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,Will you not have to be with your \N"sudden, expected loneliness"?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.55,0:08:34.24,Main,Kakeru,0000,0000,0000,,Is it still snowing?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.67,0:08:37.25,Main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,No, not anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.82,0:09:27.75,Main,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Morning, Kakeru.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.80,0:09:30.02,Main,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,That call—
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.80,0:09:33.24,Main,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Is he sleeping out again?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.94,0:09:38.68,Main,Kakeru,0000,0000,0000,,Morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.73,0:09:43.07,Main,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Can Fukami-san's parents make it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.60,0:09:44.39,Main,Kakeru,0000,0000,0000,,Probably.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.68,0:09:48.39,Main,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Let's have them come a bit early \Nand have a light meal with us.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.91,0:09:49.74,Main,Kakeru,0000,0000,0000,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.50,0:09:57.81,Italics,Kakeru,0000,0000,0000,,You're going to have a real\Ntalk with Touko, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.50,0:09:59.13,Main,Kakeru,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.43,0:10:01.13,Italics,Kakeru,0000,0000,0000,,You still can't decide?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.43,0:10:04.57,Italics,Kakeru,0000,0000,0000,,Just because you have Touko doesn't \Nmean you can't escape from {\i1}that{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.57,0:10:05.45,Main,Kakeru,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.87,0:10:06.87,Main,Kakeru,0000,0000,0000,,I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.00,0:10:38.51,Main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.83,0:10:41.96,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,You sure have guts when it really \Ncomes down to it, Onee-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.96,0:10:43.66,Main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.66,0:10:45.85,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,That was the highest compliment of the
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.85,0:10:48.47,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,Hinode-hama Middle School Girls' Swim Club.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.52,0:10:50.35,Main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.24,0:10:54.92,Main,Sachi,0000,0000,0000,,I don't have to carry it?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.31,0:10:58.79,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,This isn't a service. \NIt's just to be safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.09,0:11:01.13,Main,Sachi,0000,0000,0000,,You don't trust me?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.45,0:11:03.18,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,Honestly, I'm worried,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.18,0:11:04.70,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,but I'm not going to let you force yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.88,0:11:06.51,Main,Sachi,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.84,0:11:08.98,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,I'm here for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.09,0:11:11.98,Main,Sachi,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.28,0:11:34.86,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,Morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.61,0:11:36.71,Main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,Morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.04,0:11:37.71,Main,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.71,0:11:38.70,Main,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.70,0:11:40.95,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want breakfast.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.95,0:11:43.26,Main,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,That's pretty unusual, Hina.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.78,0:11:46.88,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,Stuff happened yesterday.\NI ate too much.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.88,0:11:48.38,Main,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,"Stuff"? What?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.66,0:11:50.18,Main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,I'll have lots.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.56,0:11:52.02,Main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so hungry.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.02,0:11:53.77,Main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,It looks so good!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.07,0:11:57.65,Main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,Mom, Hina-chan says she's not \Nhungry, so I'll have hers.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.71,0:12:14.36,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,Use that root.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.68,0:12:27.30,Hinode Dance School,Text,0000,0000,0000,,Hinode Dance School
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.35,0:12:40.86,Main,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,Sounds good. I'd love to be there.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.18,0:12:42.56,Main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,What about you, Mom?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.56,0:12:43.49,Main,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Definitely.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.49,0:12:44.75,Main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,So we're set.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.75,0:12:46.92,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,All right! I'm going to wear that outfit.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.28,0:12:51.11,Main,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,I'll start early on work, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.11,0:12:52.75,Main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,I'll help.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.76,0:14:03.99,Main,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,What's that about?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.99,0:14:05.92,Main,Yanagi,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone's all like, "Who's that?"
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.92,0:14:08.03,Main,Yanagi,0000,0000,0000,,"What is he to you?"
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.68,0:14:10.36,Main,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.73,0:14:13.73,Main,Yanagi,0000,0000,0000,,So, what'd you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.76,0:14:15.64,Main,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,What'd I think?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.64,0:14:17.21,Main,Yanagi,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, your thoughts.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.27,0:14:22.71,Main,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,You danced the best out of everyone \Nthere, and you were the prettiest.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.86,0:14:28.89,Main,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,You're
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.36,0:14:31.62,Main,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,leaving after you graduate, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.56,0:14:39.43,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,Hey,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.91,0:14:43.07,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,I did my best yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.00,0:14:48.67,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,Are you going to \NHinode-hama High School
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.67,0:14:50.15,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,with Onee-chan starting next semester?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.38,0:14:52.63,Main,Kakeru,0000,0000,0000,,That's my plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.91,0:14:56.04,Main,Kakeru,0000,0000,0000,,I haven't officially transferred yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.04,0:14:57.29,Main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,What are you two talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.45,0:15:00.08,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,He's all yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.83,0:15:02.71,Main,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,Would you like cake?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.70,0:15:05.08,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,I'll have some!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.38,0:15:07.17,Main,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,Kakeru, how about you guys?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.17,0:15:09.86,Main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, we're going for a walk.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.95,0:15:12.89,Main,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,I'm starting by 5:30.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.89,0:15:13.60,Main,Kakeru,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.66,0:15:19.68,Main,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,Are you sure you want to run with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.26,0:15:22.01,Main,Yanagi,0000,0000,0000,,No one said that.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.31,0:15:24.19,Main,Yanagi,0000,0000,0000,,I just got into a habit of running.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.47,0:15:42.33,Main,Sachi,0000,0000,0000,,Here you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.34,0:15:46.13,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,It's really good!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.91,0:15:49.04,Main,Sachi,0000,0000,0000,,These are Chinese onions, tomatoes,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.04,0:15:50.87,Main,Sachi,0000,0000,0000,,and boiled spinach.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.87,0:15:53.78,Main,Sachi,0000,0000,0000,,Deep-fried vegetables and fried eggs.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.42,0:15:56.89,Main,Sachi,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, chopsticks.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.50,0:15:58.15,Main,Sachi,0000,0000,0000,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.15,0:15:59.21,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.56,0:16:04.57,Main,Sachi,0000,0000,0000,,The other day,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.27,0:16:07.40,Main,Sachi,0000,0000,0000,,at Kirinkan...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.40,0:16:09.58,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, what about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.78,0:16:12.49,Main,Sachi,0000,0000,0000,,There was something I couldn't say.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.94,0:16:16.74,Main,Sachi,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.18,0:16:25.78,Main,Sachi,0000,0000,0000,,I did something awful, and \NI got you wound up in it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.94,0:16:27.79,Main,Sachi,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.45,0:16:33.14,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,Sure,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.58,0:16:36.08,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,this hike, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.16,0:16:38.58,Main,Sachi,0000,0000,0000,,"For tomorrow."
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.54,0:16:42.82,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,It is, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.07,0:16:51.23,Main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,I've always been seeing shiny things,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.23,0:16:54.70,Main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,partly because of my dad's \Njob as a glassblower.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.44,0:16:58.70,Main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know what they are again.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.10,0:17:01.85,Main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder when I started seeing them.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.71,0:17:06.23,Main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,Can I see that for a second?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.81,0:17:07.71,Main,Kakeru,0000,0000,0000,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.18,0:17:16.32,Main,Kakeru,0000,0000,0000,,Our experiment's about to begin.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.00,0:17:18.86,Main,Kakeru,0000,0000,0000,,I hope we learn something.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.86,0:17:20.83,Main,Kakeru,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, but
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.19,0:17:23.19,Main,Kakeru,0000,0000,0000,,maybe we don't have to.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.77,0:17:26.94,Main,Kakeru,0000,0000,0000,,I never thought our families would
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.94,0:17:29.08,Main,Kakeru,0000,0000,0000,,get together to listen \Nto my mom play piano.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.63,0:17:31.66,Main,Kakeru,0000,0000,0000,,But maybe
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.14,0:17:34.34,Main,Kakeru,0000,0000,0000,,that's enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.79,0:17:36.89,Main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,Kakeru-kun, are you—
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.19,0:17:37.84,Main,Kakeru,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.79,0:17:40.35,Main,Kakeru,0000,0000,0000,,I think I'm afraid.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.08,0:18:10.96,Main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,Can you see it too, Kakeru-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.96,0:18:11.71,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.42,0:18:38.56,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,Your knees get so messed\Nup on the way down.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.82,0:18:48.77,Main,Sachi,0000,0000,0000,,Can you hear my voice?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.70,0:18:51.66,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I can.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.06,0:18:55.72,Main,Sachi,0000,0000,0000,,The other person is nearby, \Nbut you can't see her.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.06,0:18:57.46,Main,Sachi,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't that weird?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.69,0:19:01.02,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,Can you see me?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.03,0:19:04.38,Main,Sachi,0000,0000,0000,,I can't see too well yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.92,0:19:15.75,Main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.73,0:19:20.33,Main,Kakeru,0000,0000,0000,,I think I might be afraid to be with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.36,0:19:23.87,Main,Kakeru,0000,0000,0000,,Mom's asking me if I want to
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.87,0:19:26.76,Main,Kakeru,0000,0000,0000,,go on tour with her around the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.28,0:19:29.53,Main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,Kakeru-kun, what are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.53,0:19:33.06,Main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,Are you saying you might leave soon?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.11,0:19:37.01,Main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,I think I've had enough of experiencing
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.01,0:19:39.82,Main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,the sudden, expected loneliness.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.85,0:19:46.03,Main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,But we were together all day yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.52,0:19:51.22,Main,Kakeru,0000,0000,0000,,I'm home.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.07,0:19:55.70,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,Onee-chan, come on! We're starting.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.36,0:20:01.97,Main,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,Have a seat over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.40,0:20:09.02,Main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,If that's really a fragment of the future,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.15,0:20:13.48,Main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,it means we'll see the fireworks \Ntogether next year, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.87,0:20:44.77,Main,Sachi,0000,0000,0000,,Once we're down the mountain, \NI want to go to Kazemichi.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.77,0:20:45.72,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,Sure thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.06,0:20:57.06,Main,Yanagi,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.22,0:21:01.30,Main,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,I need to talk to Touko again.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.49,0:21:08.12,Main,Yanagi,0000,0000,0000,,It's been a while. How about \Nwe go to Kazemichi later?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.49,0:21:09.26,Main,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.70,0:23:32.79,Main,Kakeru,0000,0000,0000,,Just hurry up and introduce yourselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.79,0:23:33.84,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Hiro Shirosaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.84,0:23:34.77,Main,Yanagi,0000,0000,0000,,Yanagi Takayama.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.77,0:23:36.04,Main,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Yukinari Imi.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.04,0:23:37.80,Main,Sachi,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Sachi Nagamiya.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.80,0:23:39.85,Main,Yanagi,0000,0000,0000,,Um, you can see me?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.06,0:23:39.85,Episode-Title,,0000,0000,0000,,Episode 12\N"Fireworks (Once Again)"
